Once upon a time, there lived a monkey.Below the tree,there was a lake in which a crocodile was living.
Monkey and crocodile became good friends and soon monkey used to share the fruits on the tree with the crocodile.
The crocodile's wife was very greedy and wanted to eat the monkey when she heard about him.crocodile
warned her that its not correct but then the wife didn't listen to him.So, she planned to bring the monkey 
home along with him offering a party on hte pretext of which they planned to eat monkey.